 Town** has seen the strongest cumulative price growth since 2015\n- **Durban** has lagged significantly, with the lowest current index\n- All metros show post-2020 acceleration followed by softening into 2024\n\n::: {.callout-tip}\n## Interact with the charts\nClick a city name in the legend to hide/show it. Drag on the chart to zoom in.\nDouble-click to reset the view.\n:::\n",
